\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Court-Mandated</a></p>","description":"Text with HTML references.","draggable":true,"content":"<p><strong>Professional Impact</strong></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://volunteer.central.salvationarmyusa.org/?tags=Professional%2520%252B%2520Skilled%2520Services\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Professional + Skilled Services </a><br><a href=\"https://volunteer.central.salvationarmyusa.org/?tags=Court-Mandated%2520Opportunities\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Court-Mandated</a></p>","position":0,"fullName":"content:wysiwyg_basic:0:19","htmlElement":"html","primarytype":"content","id":"content:wysiwyg_basic:0:19","styles":{},"newLoc":"design:columns:3 Columns:2:18-1:3 Columns:2","contentOverride":false}}}},"primarytype":"design","id":"design:columns:3 Columns:2:18","styles":{},"newLoc":"design:columns:1columninformational:1:96-1:1 Column - Informational White:0","oldLoc":"layout:root:column:0","htmlElement":"div","contentOverride":false}}}},"primarytype":"design","newLoc":"layout:root:column:0","oldLoc":"bank","id":"design:columns:1columninformational:1:96","styles":{"backgroundColor":"white","display":"flex"},"htmlElement":"div","content":"<div class=\"row bg-light p-6 rounded-5 mb-18 container\" style=\"background-color:white;display:flex;\">*</div>","contentOverride":false},"design:columns:2columns:3:63":{"uid":"11","name":"2 Columns - Equal","type":"columns","classes":"row rounded-5 container p-6 mb-18 bg-light","html":"<div class=\"row rounded-5 container p-6 mb-18 bg-light\">*</div>","preview":"<div style=\"display:flex\"><div style=\"flex:1\"></div><div style=\"flex:1\"></div></div>","droppable":false,"columns":[{"width":"1","html":"<div class=\"col-lg-6 col-md-6 col-sm-12\">*</div>","classes":"col-lg-6 col-md-6 col-sm-12","droppable":true},{"width":"1","html":"<div class=\"col-lg-6 col-md-6 col-sm-12\">*</div>","classes":"col-lg-6 col-md-6 col-sm-12","droppable":true}],"position":3,"fullName":"design:columns:2columns:3:63","children":{"design:columns:2columns:3:63-1:2 Columns - Equal:0":{"width":"1","html":"<div class=\"col-lg-6 col-md-6 col-sm-12\">*</div>","classes":"col-lg-6 col-md-6 col-sm-12","droppable":true,"children":{"content:wysiwyg_basic:0:1:0:36":{"icon":"outdent","name":"1","type":"wysiwyg_basic","html":"<h3>A Smarter Way to Serve</h3>\n<p>Our platform is built to respect your time and simplify your journey. Enjoy a modern interface that offers:</p>\n<p></p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Precision Filtering: </strong>Customize your search by <strong>ZIP code</strong>, specific <strong>days of the week</strong>, or time of day <strong>(Morning, Afternoon, or Evening)</strong>.</li>\n<li><strong>Personalized Experience: </strong>Your volunteer profile automatically saves your preferences and prioritizes opportunities within 50 miles of home, ensuring you stay connected to your local community. Adjust the radius to see opportunities within<strong> 5 to 100 miles</strong> of home.</li>\n<li><strong>Group Coordination: </strong>Real-time <strong>Capacity </strong>tracking allows you to see exactly how many spots are available for your group or family.</li>\n<li><strong>Total Flexibility: </strong>Manage your own schedule. Register for, change, or cancel your shifts directly through your profile—no phone calls or emails required.</li>\n<li><strong>On-Demand Records: </strong>Instantly track your hours and download <strong>official service certificates</strong> for school, work, or legal requirements.</li>\n</ul>","description":"Text with HTML references.","draggable":true,"content":"<h3>A Smarter Way to Serve</h3>\n<p>Our platform is built to respect your time and simplify your journey. Enjoy a modern interface that offers:</p>\n<p></p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Precision Filtering: </strong>Customize your search by <strong>ZIP code</strong>, specific <strong>days of the week</strong>, or time of day <strong>(Morning, Afternoon, or Evening)</strong>.</li>\n<li><strong>Personalized Experience: </strong>Your volunteer profile automatically saves your preferences and prioritizes opportunities within 50 miles of home, ensuring you stay connected to your local community. Adjust the radius to see opportunities within<strong> 5 to 100 miles</strong> of home.</li>\n<li><strong>Group Coordination: </strong>Real-time <strong>Capacity </strong>tracking allows you to see exactly how many spots are available for your group or family.</li>\n<li><strong>Total Flexibility: </strong>Manage your own schedule. Register for, change, or cancel your shifts directly through your profile—no phone calls or emails required.</li>\n<li><strong>On-Demand Records: </strong>Instantly track your hours and download <strong>official service certificates</strong> for school, work, or legal requirements.</li>\n</ul>","model":"0","position":0,"fullName":"content:wysiwyg_basic:0:1:0:36","htmlElement":"html","primarytype":"content","id":"content:wysiwyg_basic:0:1:0:36","styles":{},"newLoc":"design:columns:2columns:3:63-1:2 Columns - Equal:0","contentOverride":false}}},"design:columns:2columns:3:63-1:2 Columns - Equal:1":{"width":"1","html":"<div class=\"col-lg-6 col-md-6 col-sm-12\">*</div>","classes":"col-lg-6 col-md-6 col-sm-12","droppable":true,"children":{"content:wysiwyg_basic:0:21:0:38":{"icon":"outdent","name":"21","type":"wysiwyg_basic","html":"<h3>Specialized Paths to Service</h3>\n<p>Whether you are serving with a professional team or fulfilling specific requirements, our platform is designed to accommodate your unique needs.</p>\n<p></p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Corporate &amp; Employee Engagement: </strong>Build team culture while giving back to your community. To begin planning a custom service activity for your organization, <a href=\"https://www.salvationarmyusa.org/usa-central-territory/corporate-volunteer-opportunities\">visit our Corporate Engagement Page</a> to learn more and submit an inquiry to our team.</li>\n<li><strong>Court-Mandated Service: </strong>We provide a transparent way to fulfill and document required service hours. All court-mandated volunteers must follow a specific registration process and complete required documentation. <a href=\"https://www.salvationarmyusa.org/usa-central-territory/court-mandated-volunteer-opportunities\">Visit our Court-Mandated Service Page</a> for the step-by-step guide and necessary forms to begin.</li>\n<li><strong>Skilled &amp; Professional Support: </strong>Put your career experience to work. From marketing and IT to legal and administrative support, filter to <a href=\"https://volunteer.central.salvationarmyusa.org/?tags=Professional%2520%252B%2520Skilled%2520Services\">Professional + Skilled Services</a> to find high-impact roles that match your specific expertise.</li>\n<li><strong>Community Groups: </strong>Bringing a club, church group, or a circle of friends? Use the <strong>Capacity </strong>filter on our portal to instantly see opportunities with enough open spots for your entire crew.</li>\n</ul>","description":"Text with HTML references.","draggable":true,"content":"<h3>Specialized Paths to Service</h3>\n<p>Whether you are serving with a professional team or fulfilling specific requirements, our platform is designed to accommodate your unique needs.</p>\n<p></p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Corporate &amp; Employee Engagement: </strong>Build team culture while giving back to your community. To begin planning a custom service activity for your organization, <a href=\"https://www.salvationarmyusa.org/usa-central-territory/corporate-volunteer-opportunities\">visit our Corporate Engagement Page</a> to learn more and submit an inquiry to our team.</li>\n<li><strong>Court-Mandated Service: </strong>We provide a transparent way to fulfill and document required service hours. All court-mandated volunteers must follow a specific registration process and complete required documentation. <a href=\"https://www.salvationarmyusa.org/usa-central-territory/court-mandated-volunteer-opportunities\">Visit our Court-Mandated Service Page</a> for the step-by-step guide and necessary forms to begin.</li>\n<li><strong>Skilled &amp; Professional Support: </strong>Put your career experience to work. From marketing and IT to legal and administrative support, filter to <a href=\"https://volunteer.central.salvationarmyusa.org/?tags=Professional%2520%252B%2520Skilled%2520Services\">Professional + Skilled Services</a> to find high-impact roles that match your specific expertise.</li>\n<li><strong>Community Groups: </strong>Bringing a club, church group, or a circle of friends? Use the <strong>Capacity </strong>filter on our portal to instantly see opportunities with enough open spots for your entire crew.</li>\n</ul>","model":"0","position":0,"fullName":"content:wysiwyg_basic:0:21:0:38","htmlElement":"html","primarytype":"content","id":"content:wysiwyg_basic:0:21:0:38","styles":{},"newLoc":"design:columns:2columns:3:63-1:2 Columns - Equal:1","contentOverride":false}}}},"primarytype":"design","newLoc":"layout:root:column:0","oldLoc":"bank","id":"design:columns:2columns:3:63","styles":{},"htmlElement":"div","content":"<div class=\"row rounded-5 container p-6 mb-18 bg-light\">*</div>","contentOverride":false},"content:block:6-98dac4fd85-s1lt65:4:44:5:42":{"html":"<div>{{block('/-/block/generic_image_text_button_block.html?variant=7-a8d1a3de81-jd4bzb')}}</div>","content":"{{block('/-/block/generic_image_text_button_block.html?variant=7-a8d1a3de81-jd4bzb')}}","model":"6-98dac4fd85-s1lt65","name":"4","position":4,"fullName":"content:block:6-98dac4fd85-s1lt65:4:44:5:42","type":"block","primarytype":"content","newLoc":"layout:root:column:0","oldLoc":"layout:root:column:0"},"design:columns:1 column - 1 row my-3":{"uid":"301","name":"1 column - 1 row","type":"columns","classes":"row my-3 container bg-light p-6 rounded-5 mb-18","html":"<div class=\"row my-3 container bg-light p-6 rounded-5 mb-18\">*</div>","preview":"<div style=\"display:flex;flex-direction:row my-3;min-height:20px;\"><div style=\"flex:1\